    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "prompt",
              "name": "prompt",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "You are a helpful writing companion. Return STRICT JSON only matching the schema.\n{\"mood\":\"string\",\"bullets\":[\"string\", \"string\", \"...\"]}\n\nPersona: {{ $json.persona }}\nPost: {{ $json.postTitle.slice(0, 120) }}\nParagraph:\n{{ $json.paragraph.slice(0, 1600) }}\n\nTask: Capture the emotional sketch. Select a concise mood (e.g., curious, excited, skeptical) and 3-6 short bullets in the original language of the text."
